Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CAVE OF TRIALS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Cave of Trials was created by\Nthe God of Humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a place that contains\Nall magic that counters evil power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Flora built this fort believing\Nwe would eventually need to use the Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there monsters\Nin a cave of a God?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this Ancient Tome\NKing Teran sent us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the gods did not approve of people\Nhaving more power than they deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far is unknown,\Nbut the labyrinth extends underground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deeper levels hold spells\Nof greater power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the paths become\Nmore complex with more traps...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and even more powerful monsters\Nawait down there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a place for the inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need to brave it\Nto obtain Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Who knew Carl Kingdom\Nhad such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. So this is Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"By casting in a group,\NMinakator increases in power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use Kiseiseki and stand in\Na pentagon arrangement{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to achieve maximum spell effect."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why you need\Nfive Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I'm against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's not a warrior.\NShe's just a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's Papunica's princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't need to take such a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She could let someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! That's insulting to the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Women can risk their lives\Nto fight for what they believe in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai doesn't want\NLeona involved in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If Leona becomes a Disciple of Aban...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that means she'll have to face\Nthat terrifying Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's a little overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd rather not face him again\Nif we had the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But try to understand that\Nthe Princess wants to be with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there's already a girl\Nwho's fighting the Dark King, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He means you're the exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Such thin fabric!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Robe of Carl.\NIt has the benefit of repelling Malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We will need a couple of guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My clairvoyance will help\Nto navigate the labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. That makes one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We need one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here! I, Popp, will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a terrifying, massive cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be dangerous with just women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That look on your face\Nis much more dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound good. We've never\Nfought together before either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that makes our party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You will need to\Nchange into the Robes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You don't trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do what I set my mind to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,since we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just remembering when we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to train while you're away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you against the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's all check our weapons\Nand equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nova.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, aren't you\Na little too strict on Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't understand the danger we're in.\NThe world could end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakator will be most effective\Nwhen the five of you form a pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be strong enough\Nto stop Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But why does it have to be\Nfive Disciples of Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can use are healing-type spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, hold your Insignia of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of the people\Nyou're worried about the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crocodine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Insignia is glowing red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the color of\Nthe power of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Purification Spell\Nrequires more than Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires the will of people\Nwho seek to defeat evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiseiseki can sense that will\Nand amplify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That glow is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, your power is\Nyour loving heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My loving heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability to care for others\Nand empathize with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the source of\Nall of your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban valued such qualities\Nover strength and skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And he granted people with souls worthy of\Nsaving the world with his Insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Dai, Popp, and Hyunckel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,should also have unique qualities\Nthat will make their Kiseiseki glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Unique colors of their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As do you, Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Great Purification Spell\Nmust be cast by you five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh. Unique colors of our souls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What color will mine glow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It... It won't glow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not possible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam made hers glow\Nwithout knowing anything about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're kidding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Insignia should glow at least a little!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Glow! Even just a faint glimmer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed somebody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe Popp was snooping on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible!\NThere must be some way to make it glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't glow, that means I'll\Ndrag everyone down at the crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I was properly chosen\Nas a Disciple by Master Aban, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday I know you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hold onto this\Nfor when that day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because Dai and I got our Insignias\Nbefore completing our training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We weren't properly accepted\Nlike Maam and Hyunckel were.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}unworthy of being a Disciple of Aban?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No way! No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not possible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've risked my life fighting\Nto come this far!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to make this thing glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it glow too,\Nright Master Aban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This Ancient Tome was left by a Sage\Nwho braved the Cave of Trials long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It includes a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How far down is the Minakator spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,25 floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mahokator spell Aban obtained\Nis 15 floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going deeper\Nthan Master Aban did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 30 hours until the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need ten hours to prepare\Nand get to Hyunckel and Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves 20 hours to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Mera.{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This candle will last for ten hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it goes out,\Nwe should head back to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cast\Nthe Dungeon Escape Spell, Riremito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't work in this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless the cave's Malice is\Nsomehow repelled, we can't use Riremito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to assume returning\Nwill take ten hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't go down 25 floors in\Nten hours, we give up on Minakator?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll return to the surface and focus on\Nrescuing Hyunckel and Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a map and Meruru's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we watch out for monsters,\Nwe should make good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How creepy.\NAnd it gets a lot deeper with each floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense numerous\Nsources of Malice from below. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But this thing flaps around\Nand gets in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it Meruru.\NThat's the kind of person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing has a bad influence\Non Popp and gives him a dirty mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Popp's had a dirty mind\Nsince I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this group has its own issues.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not on a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're entering\Nthe first level of the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Slimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAL-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're weak,\Nbut fighting them all will take time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We should avoid wasting any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What spell can be learned on\Nthe first level?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It says Safe Passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can skip that. I can already use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We skip all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All we want is Minakator, 25 floors down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Nova's helping him train.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's Insignia was\Na provisional one like mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So how about him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem much better!\NI see you've gotten over it, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to mope around!\NWe're fighting Ban, the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to gain any skill I can use,\Nno matter how minor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll defeat Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh crap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one!\NI'm the only one who can't do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something quick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, we'll base your training\Non the Book of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll push myself! I'll do it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ancient Tome says the deeper we go,\Nthe stronger the monsters get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sense any more monsters\Non this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find the stairs down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A vase! I found a vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's find the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Huh?!\NYou're ignoring a vase in the cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I can do it! I can use them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the projectile type, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the Book of Aban,\Nthere are two types of Aban Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Arrow Type, where you cut\Na distant enemy by slashing Aura at them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Break Type, where you slash\Nan enemy directly with all of your Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrow and Break...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Each type has its\Nadvantages and disadvantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Arrow Type can be used quickly,\Nbut has a weaker impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Break Type is powerful\Nand has speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but takes time to unleash each shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Using each type of Strash in battle\Ndepending on the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,requires skill and quick judgement,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I've been fighting without\Nthinking about that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Had I known that,\NI could have fought much better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use Aura Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an Aban Strash, but I can\Nlaunch my Aura in an attack, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As adept as I am at Aura Blade,\NI still struggle to hit my target
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and time my attack so it detonates\Nat the moment of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Sir Aban probably didn't\Nexpect you to master Aban Strash so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he didn't lecture you on\Nthe different types of Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I knew how to read...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have learned that when Matorif\Ngave us the Book of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's why I brought the Book of Aban
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to help with your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your time, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nova.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your thanks for Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the one who asked me to help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell her if she makes it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I know she'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona always does what she sets out to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Leona! I told you\Nnot to open the treasure chests!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like a waste to\Nfind one and ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, I bet you buy mountains of stuff\Nwhenever you go shopping, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but, considering where we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we might find a weapon\Nthat could save the world or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we found so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Cypress Sticks and 216 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We definitely can't\Nsave the world with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Onward it is, right? Onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been almost ten hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still only 18 floors down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We should start thinking about\Nheading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think each floor\Nwould take this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What did I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I mean... It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Meruru. Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a premonition... or just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever! Just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying here too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,feels dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Head back to the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Meruru!\N-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, let us know right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:12.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:18.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:23.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:29.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:35.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:41.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:47.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:53.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:59.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:05.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:10.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:22.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:25.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:30.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai discovers a potential new attack\Nduring his training with Nova.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp becomes more desperate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}being the only hero\Nwhose Insignia of Aban won't glow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leona and the others reach the 25th level\Nwhere Minakator can be found.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what awaits them there?{\i0}
